SUMMARY:Addison C. Harris Lecture featuring Emily Bazelon
DESCRIPTION:Invited guest\, Emily Bazelon\, will present "Under Pressure:
  The Rule of Law at DOJ and DHS and the Future of Federal Law Enforcement
 " for the Spring 2026 Addison C. Harris Lecture.  In conversation with Pr
 of. Cindy Cho\, Bazelon will discuss her investigative reporting of the D
 epartment of Justice\, Department of Homeland Security\, and the Federal 
 Bureau of Investigation.&#160\;  This event is available in person and on
  Zoom.&#160\;  Register here (https://iu.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_ipO3
 8APFSni2Uj4t0glljw) for virtual attendance.&#160\;RSVP below by Tuesday\,
  March 24 to attend in person. Please note\, food is ordered only for tho
 se who RSVP.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Invited guest\, Emily Bazelon\, will pr
 esent "Under Pressure: The Rule of Law at DOJ and DHS and the Future of F
 ederal Law Enforcement" for the Spring 2026 Addison C. Harris Lecture.</p
 ><p>  In conversation with Prof. Cindy Cho\, Bazelon will discuss her inv
 estigative reporting of the Department of Justice\, Department of Homelan
 d Security\, and the Federal Bureau of Investigation.&#160\;</p><p>  This
  event is available in person and on Zoom.&#160\;</p><p>  Register <stron
 g><a href="https://iu.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_ipO38APFSni2Uj4t0glljw"
 >here</a></strong> for virtual attendance.&#160\;</p><p><strong>RSVP belo
 w by Tuesday\, March 24 to attend in person</strong>. Please note\, food 
 is ordered only for those who RSVP.&#160\;</p>
