SUMMARY:Academic Advising Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Returning JD students are invited to join the Office for Stud
 ent Affairs and the Academic Success and Bar Support program for a Zoom w
 orkshop regarding fall course registration on Wednesday\, March 25 at 5:0
 0 pm.  We will walk through graduation requirements\, academic regulation
 s\, and curricular considerations to take into account when planning a co
 urse schedule. We will also talk about what courses will best prepare stu
 dents for the doctrinal and skills portions of the bar exam. Lastly\, we 
 will discuss the new tool students will use to register for courses\, Ste
 llic\, and identify resources so that will prepare students to use it.  W
 e strongly encourage all 1Ls to attend this Zoom session since it is thei
 r first time selecting courses. We strongly encourage all 2Ls to attend s
 ince it is their first time using Stellic.RSVP on CareerNet (https://nam1
 2.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Flaw-indiana-csm.sym
 plicity.com%2Fstudents%2F%3Fs%3Devent%26ss%3Dws%26mode%3Dform%26id%3D1e66
 2951fdca166b86e6ae7c1320662f&amp\;data=05%7C02%7Ccafitzwa%40iu.edu%7Cae63
 3b7d058641c96fb908de854edc6f%7C1113be34aed14d00ab4bcdd02510be91%7C1%7C0%7
 C639094770906921825%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiO
