SUMMARY:CCD Open House
DESCRIPTION:The Center for Constitutional Democracy invites 1Ls to join a
 n information session on the Center's work. At the CCD we study\, draft\,
  and amend constitutions\, and work with governments and reformers all ov
 er the world to build legal institutions that will incentivize peaceful c
 onstitutionalism. Hear from CCD Executive Director\, Prof. David Williams
 \, and current CCD Fellows about their stories and experiences. Light sna
 cks will be provided.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The Center for Constitutional Democracy
  invites 1Ls to join an information session on the Center's work. At the 
 CCD we study\, draft\, and amend constitutions\, and work with government
 s and reformers all over the world to build legal institutions that will 
 incentivize peaceful constitutionalism. Hear from CCD Executive Director\
 , Prof. David Williams\, and current CCD Fellows about their stories and 
 experiences. Light snacks will be provided.&#160\;</p>
