SUMMARY:CLS: Operating While Intoxicated: Defense
DESCRIPTION:Join CrimSoc for an engaging discussion on Operating While In
 toxicated: Defense with an experienced criminal defense attorney. This ev
 ent will provide insight into the real-world strategies attorneys use whe
 n defending OWI cases\, from challenging traffic stops and field sobriety
  tests to negotiating outcomes and preparing cases for trial.  Our guest 
 speaker will share practical perspectives from years of courtroom experie
 nce as a prosecutor and criminal defense attorney\, discuss common issues
  that arise in OWI prosecutions\, and answer questions about practicing c
 riminal defense. This is a great opportunity for law students interested 
 in criminal law\, litigation\, and trial advocacy to learn how OWI cases 
 are built and defended.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join CrimSoc for an engaging discussion
  on Operating While Intoxicated: Defense with an experienced criminal def
 ense attorney. This event will provide insight into the real-world strate
 gies attorneys use when defending OWI cases\, from challenging traffic st
 ops and field sobriety tests to negotiating outcomes and preparing cases 
 for trial.</p><p>  Our guest speaker will share practical perspectives fr
 om years of courtroom experience as a prosecutor and criminal defense att
 orney\, discuss common issues that arise in OWI prosecutions\, and answer
  questions about practicing criminal defense. This is a great opportunity
  for law students interested in criminal law\, litigation\, and trial adv
 ocacy to learn how OWI cases are built and defended.&#160\;</p>
