 ounced when the LSSSE closes in April!)</p><p>  During the lunch hour on 
 Tuesday\, April 21\, come by starting at 12pm to get some lunch\, enjoy t
 he (hopefully) nice weather on the ground floor patio\, and celebrate the
  near-end of this academic year!&#160\;</p>
