SUMMARY:2026 Privacy Law Scholars Conference
DESCRIPTION:A national rotating conference\, the 2026 Privacy Law Scholar
 s Conference will take place May 28 - 29 at Indiana University Maurer Sch
 ool of Law\, with a pre-conference mentoring session on May 27.  Since 20
 08\, PLSC has assembled a wide array of privacy law scholars and practiti
 oners from around the world to discuss current issues in information priv
 acy law and policy.  For more information and to register visit the PLSC 
 main page (https://privacyscholars.org/).
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  A national rotating conference\, the 20
 26 Privacy Law Scholars Conference will take place May 28 - 29 at Indiana
  University Maurer School of Law\, with a pre-conference mentoring sessio
 n on May 27.</p><p>  Since 2008\, PLSC has assembled a wide array of priv
 acy law scholars and practitioners from around the world to discuss curre
 nt issues in information privacy law and policy.</p><p>  For more informa
 tion and to register visit the <a href="https://privacyscholars.org/" tar
 get="_blank" rel="noopener">PLSC main page</a>.</p>
